Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:17.22,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,誰にも見せられないもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:22.33,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,頭の中溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:28.12,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,間違いさえも無い世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.58,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,迷い込んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.98,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,あり得ないほど擦り込まれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.09,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,目に見えるものだけの“世界”現象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.94,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,暴きだせるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.58,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,Plastic Tac Tic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.21,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,もう誰もおかしくなれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.92,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,貴様もplastic beautiful world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.66,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,美しすぎる世界に　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.73,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,僕はなぜか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.78,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,光が見えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:11.44,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,破裂していく心が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.53,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,無限のリフレクション
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:22.74,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,secret remains for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.24,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,見せかけの色と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.46,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,未来を暴かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.74,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,keep it secret motion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,JP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,JP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,JP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:17.22,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,脑海里充斥着的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:22.33,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都无法看见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:28.12,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这个不会犯错的机械世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:31.58,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,一路行走一路彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.98,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,与你擦肩而过的次数多到近乎异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:46.09,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我眼里能看到的 就是我全部的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:48.94,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,能否打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.58,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,plastic tac tic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.21,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都习以为常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.92,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样 plastic beautiful world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:59.85,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个过于完美的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.73,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:06.78,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到光明的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.88,0:02:11.44,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,心在一步步碎裂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.53,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,回音无限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:38.96,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:22.74,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,为你留下这个秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.24,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,徒有其表的鲜艳色彩及未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:33.46,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,别打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.74,Op-cn,NTP,0,0,0,,就让这个秘密继续秘密下去
